Ombi is your friendly media request tool, automatically syncs with
your media with your media servers!

You'll need to create a ombi user in order to run with the provided init
script:

# groupadd ombi
# useradd -r -d /var/lib/ombi -g ombi ombi

Optionally change these by:

OMBI_USER=user OMBI_GROUP=group ./ombi.Slackbuild

